Articles.Content:
Being stuck with the free demo that is v0.13.3, I'v had an interesting time finding compatible mods. I figure that I can't be the only one in the same predicament. So I decided to build a repository of mods for the demo. If anyone has any additions, feel free to post them.

Here they are. All the Mods that I have found so far for KSP v0.13.3 I'll update this post whenever I find more. At some point, I'll even make it all pretty.

[snip]

http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/forum/showthread.php/4275-cBBp-SPC-Pack-v0-4-Fixed-Failcan-RCS-and-added-some-adapter-pieces-Enjoy?highlight=failcan

http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/forum/showthread.php/9434-0-14-ver-1-1-Wacky-Wood-Wares!-Cartoony-Parts-for-increased-Kerbalness?highlight=wacky+wood+wares

http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/forum/showthread.php/4530-Closed-Amphibious-Gear-and-the-Drone?highlight=gemini

http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/forum/showthread.php/5609-HSTW-1-75m-Gemini?highlight=gemini

(Note: The above link is a list of mods with descriptions and links. Some of them are broken., but most of them are ok. Just watch out for the iLivid download page. It's a malware trojan.)
